    "name": "StableCoin-ConcentrationDrift-30d-iter5",
    "description": "APPROACH 3 iter5 — CONCENTRATION DRIFT MODEL (6.5): HHI across 7-instrument portfolio.\n\nPortfolio: $101,000 reserves (7 instruments) / $100,000 token supply\n  Bucket         | Day 1 Amount | Share  | HQLA\n  CASH (2 instr) |  $23,000     | 22.8%  | L1\n  4W_TBILL       |  $10,000     |  9.9%  | L1  (matures day 18)\n  13W_TBILL      |  $32,000     | 31.7%  | L1\n  26W_TBILL      |  $26,000     | 25.7%  | L1\n  COMMPAPER      |   $6,000     |  5.9%  | L2A\n  DEFI           |   $4,000     |  4.0%  | L2B\n\nStarting HHI = 0.02^2 + ... sum of squares = ~0.185\n  (well diversified: HHI < hhiWarningThreshold=0.35)\n\nSTRESS SCENARIO — REDEMPTION DRAINS CASH:\n  Days 1-10:   Normal. Cash drain ~$600/day from redemption pressure\n  Days 11-18:  HALT PERIOD — heavy redemption drains cash rapidly\n               Cash bucket: $23k -> $17k = 22.8% -> 17.0%\n               Other buckets hold (T-bills not liquidated)\n               HHI rises as cash share drops, 13W tbill dominates\n  Day 18:      tbill-4wk-001 matures -> +$10k cash injected\n               Cash: $17k -> $27k = 17.0% -> 26.7%\n               HHI improves (4 buckets more balanced)\n  Days 19-30:  Recovery rolling — new 4wk tbill purchased\n               HHI returns toward baseline\n\nKEY CHANGE vs stablecoin-1:\n  7 buckets (not 4): CASH, 4W, 13W, 26W, COMMPAPER, DEFI, NEW_TBILL\n  maxSingleAssetShare=0.35 (not 0.40 — tighter for GENIUS/MiCA)\n  hhiWarningThreshold=0.30 (not 0.35 — more sensitive)\n  Realistic bucket sizes from actual iter5 portfolio\n  13W tbill $32k = 31.7% share is largest single bucket\n\nOpen Postman Console (Ctrl+Alt+C) before running.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
